{"tid":847868,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【最後身影曝光】下水救人遇可怕激流 大馬6消防壯烈殉職","createTime":"2018-10-04T13:13:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-04T13:30:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a7932decceccd8aaa280f4667faa5ce7a5c691fb","tid":847868,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T13:13:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181004/58755011\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181004%2F58755011&d=2aUCrxJkkAbkNzL89I8rYVeK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=bf0df90d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181004%2F58755011&h=910e92cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181004/58755011</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年10月04日 <br />\n<br />\n【最後身影曝光】下水救人遇可怕激流 大馬6消防壯烈殉職<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n建立時間 (HKT): 1004<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n馬來西亞雪蘭莪州一名17歲少年周三與兩名朋友到一個廢棄的礦湖釣魚，不幸失足墮湖。6名消防員潛入水中搜索時不幸遇上漩渦，潛水裝備被沖走，6人全部溺斃殉職。<br />\n<br />\n殉職消防員出事前的片段曝光，他們下水後遇上激流，根本完全無法穩住身體。他們只有一個救生圈，在水中掙扎大約兩分鐘後沉入水中，拍攝者驚覺出事即中斷拍攝。6人被救起時已失去知覺，他們年齡介乎24至34歲。<br />\n<br />\n消防局周三下午5時接報少年失蹤，派出15名消防員到現場搜救。消防員到場後，6名蛙人穿上全副裝備，並且繫上繩索下水搜尋。警方表示︰「湖內水流湍急洶湧，6人迅即被捲入漩渦中，在場其他消防員發現情況不妙，立即派人查看，最後發現他們被急流沖走溺斃湖中。」<br />\n<br />\n而失蹤的少年目前仍下落不明，由於現場入夜後光線不足，為了搜救人員安全，救援行動在凌晨1時30分暫停，直至今晨才恢復。<br />\n馬來西亞《中國報》/《東方網》/英國廣播公司 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181004/large/1538655210_9315.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181004%2Flarge%2F1538655210_9315.jpg&h=7fa8cb60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n6名消防員遇上急流不幸溺斃<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181004/large/1538638417_8735.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181004%2Flarge%2F1538638417_8735.jpg&h=68ccbba7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n消防員為搜尋失蹤少年（左圖）殉職<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181004/large/1538638417_4bcb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181004%2Flarge%2F1538638417_4bcb.jpg&h=105adfc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n他們被救上岸時已失去知覺<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n【短片】仲唔係呢鋪？一跑最強欄位 「星」之馬即刻紅起來<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n【短片】二創抗衡劉德華！譚凱邦倡限外來人口 斥填海建人工島「完結香港」"},{"pid":"8ac4ac8f84f8f844fab2f936a4303601d319843d","tid":847868,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T13:17:03.000Z","msg":"rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n願上蒼保佑"},{"pid":"a8c16b576178f0518032cb051cdfecdef946c200","tid":847868,"uid":47259,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T13:30:37.000Z","msg":"累街坊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}